  <!-- ===== History Section ===== -->
  <section class="history-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro">
        <h2>The Legacy of Legend College of Health Sciences</h2>
        <p>
          Since its founding, Legend College of Health Sciences has stood as a pillar of academic
          and professional excellence in healthcare education. With a focus on innovation, research,
          and community impact, the College continues to shape the future of medical and health science
          professionals across Africa and beyond.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item left">
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>2005 – Foundation</h3>
            <p>
              Legend College of Health Sciences began its journey with a vision to train highly skilled
              healthcare professionals, driven by a mission to improve health systems and patient care.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item right">
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>2010 – Expansion</h3>
            <p>
              The college expanded its academic programs, introducing new departments such as Nursing,
              Public Health, and Medical Laboratory Science, which increased enrollment and visibility.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item left">
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>2015 – Accreditation</h3>
            <p>
              Recognized by key education and health authorities, Legend College achieved full accreditation,
              marking a major milestone in its pursuit of quality education.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item right">
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>2020 – Technology Integration</h3>
            <p>
              The institution embraced digital learning technologies, upgrading laboratories, classrooms,
              and virtual platforms to align with global educational standards.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item left">
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Today</h3>
            <p>
              Legend College of Health Sciences stands as a modern institution of repute, producing
              professionals who are redefining healthcare across the nation and beyond.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

